      "content": "hey, i got this crazy headache started out of nowhere like 20 mins ago. it's like the worst one i've ever had, feels super intense. and i noticed in the mirror my left cheek looks a little bit different? like a bit droopy? i get migraines a lot so maybe it's just a really bad one or a weird aura thing? what do u think?",
